not a true story;

a girl who we will call kayla (10 years) was with her cousins at a cabin. one night they were bored so a girl called jane (13 years) downloaded a ghost tracker and told all the girls that they could look for ghosts just for fun. The rest agreed and they went outside. they expected nothing but to their shock the tracker detected something and stared beeping.  Everyone got scared and moved closer to the bushes (the tracker detected it there) and heard something coming from there. everyone started screaming and ran away to the cabin and left kayla there. Obviously she was scared and started crying until she heard rustling from the bushes. then something jumped on her and took her inside the bushes. the rest of the cousins realized she was missing and went back outside but she wasnt here. all they heard were shrieks and cries from the bushes and decided to go in. but then as they were thinking that she cant be dead since it was her crying, they saw flesh and blood on the floor and hanging from the tree's branches....

100 LIKES FOR PART 2!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
